{"tid":1003330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中美貿易會談　中國代表在美步出酒店　受衝擊　抗議驅趕低端人口","createTime":"2019-01-31T14:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T14:44:52.000Z","uid":47714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"667696f265a476c79dd35ada20d2196fa5767d32","tid":1003330,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:37:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/2264385110267876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fposts%2F2264385110267876&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=5dc8f2da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/2264385110267876</a><br />\n<br />\n#有片 #中美貿易會談<br />\n中國代表團一步出酒店，即刻受到當地華人 熱烈「招呼」，戰狼冇出現，反而係美國保安人員保護中國代表團...<br />\n<br />\n抗議行動係關於中國早前驅趕 #低端人口 嘅暴行。<br />\n／The protesters, who said they were from Shanghai, distributed documents accusing the government of forcing Chinese residents to relocate. A woman was knocked down in the scuffle, but no one appeared to be injured.／<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BloombergTV/status/1090639740498411520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBloombergTV%2Fstatus%2F1090639740498411520&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=e715ae53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBloombergTV%2Fstatus%2F1090639740498411520&h=802553bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BloombergTV/status/1090639740498411520</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DyK7DviVAAYmMSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDyK7DviVAAYmMSB.jpg&h=4b8297a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"127444de64a0c1190595d5967053791f736bdd0a","tid":1003330,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:44:52.000Z","msg":"佢哋做咗美國嘅低端人口<img src=\"/asset